{"type":"message","id":"7d9c894b","parentId":"0f9b38bb","timestamp":"2026-05-02T03:04:49.049Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby wants to know how to give me the iCloud app password again. He needs to generate a new app-specific password from Apple and then share it with me. I should tell him the steps.\n","thinkingSignature":"f8c1cf902143a671e15691401d506ca6e5b6365ae54f28469eca9ef1b7a0e095"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nEasy:\n\n1. Go to **appleid.apple.com** → Sign in → **App-Specific Passwords** → Generate a new one (name it something like \"Emmy\")\n2. Send it to me here\n\nOnce you do that, I'll store it securely and update the email check to pull from both accounts again."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":35873,"output":109,"cacheRead":64,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36046,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777691080652,"responseId":"06449cc9706828adb3d956bc3647e3ee"}}
