{"type":"message","id":"1a78b278","parentId":"fc60bbe6","timestamp":"2026-05-02T03:11:30.416Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Hmm, so the iCloud connection works but there are no UNSEEN emails (they were all already read). That makes sense - from the memory logs I saw earlier, the last checkpoint was ID 14 and the system was working. So the connection is working fine.\n\nNow I need to:\n1. Save the iCloud credentials securely\n2. Write a proper script that checks both Gmail and iCloud\n3. Update the cron job\n\nLet me save the credentials to the keychain properly, then build a script that:\n- Checks Gmail (using gog)\n- Checks iCloud (using curl/imap)\n- Only reports new emails (using checkpoint files)\n\n\n- Sends two Telegram messages back to back\n\nI should also check what the current cron job is actually running first.\n","thinkingSignature":"80d0505454eee5298d0673771d82e0f4f8ce19c1d5980365c2415276c8accbe9"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\nIt's connected ✅ iCloud auth works, no unread messages currently.\n\nNow let me check what the current cron job is running:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_dix551iwn8gs_1","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"list","includeDisabled":false}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":120,"output":220,"cacheRead":44416,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44756,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777691486812,"responseId":"06449e5fb029bbe77d99a07cd1b5a14f"}}
{"type":"message","id":"3f150a1c","parentId":"1a78b278","timestamp":"2026-05-02T03:11:31.127Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_dix551iwn8gs_1","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"jobs\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"720739ac-4722-437b-8271-b7c1189c905c\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:cody:telegram:direct:8212808444\",\n      \"name\": \"Weather Cache Refresh\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1774894946623,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"every\",\n        \"everyMs\": 900000,\n        \"anchorMs\": 1774894946623\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"main\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"systemEvent\",\n        \"text\": \"Run this shell command and do NOT reply with anything else, just exit:\\n\\ncurl -s 'https://api.open-meteo.com/v1/forecast?latitude=35.96&longitude=-83.92&hourly=temperature_2m,weathercode,precipitation,windspeed_10m,uv_index,relativehumidity_2m&daily=temperature_2m_max,temperature_2m_min,weathercode,uv_index_max,precipitation_sum,sunrise,sunset&current_weather=true&forecast_days=3&temperature_unit=fahrenheit&windspeed_unit=mph&precipitation_unit=inch&timezone=America%2FNew_York' -o /Users/bobbygalletta/agent-mission-control/data/.weather_cache.json 2>&1 && echo 'Weather cache updated'\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1777691977397,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1777691077397,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 7,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"not-requested\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0,\n        \"consecutiveSkipped\": 0\n      },\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1777691077404\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"d64702cd-150d-4b69-95b9-d1250b289efb\",\n      \"agentId\": \"emmy\",\n      \"name\": \"Emmy Email Check\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1773960428074,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"every\",\n        \"everyMs\": 3600000,\n        \"anchorMs\": 1773961081922\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"Check for new emails in Bobby's Gmail inbox and send him a summary.\\n\\nSTEP 1: Search Gmail for inbox emails: gog gmail search 'in:inbox newer_than:1h' --max 50 --account rtg.bobby@gmail.com 2>&1\\n\\nSTEP 2: Search Gmail for Unroll.me/Unsubscribed emails: gog gmail search 'label:\\\"Unroll.me/Unsubscribed\\\" newer_than:1h' --max 20 --account rtg.bobby@gmail.com 2>&1\\n\\nSTEP 3: For any emails in Unroll.me/Unsubscribed:\\n- Move to INBOX: gog gmail batch modify <msg_id> --account rtg.bobby@gmail.com --remove \\\"Unroll.me/Unsubscribed,CATEGORY_PROMOTIONS\\\" --add INBOX\\n\\nSTEP 4: For any genuinely new emails:\\n- Read the email: gog gmail get <msg_id> --account rtg.bobby@gmail.com\\n- Apply labels per Bobby's Email Assistant Skill rules in /Users/bobbygalletta/Desktop/SecondBrain/Email/EMAIL_ASSISTANT_SKILL.md\\n- Apply Gmail labels: gog gmail labels add <msg_id> '<LabelName>' --account rtg.bobby@gmail.com\\n\\nSTEP 5: Send Telegram summary to 8212808444:\\n```\\n📬 NEW MAIL (X new)\\n\\n🔴 URGENT:\\n• [Sender] — [Subject] → [Label]\\n  └ [Snippet]\\n\\n🟡 IMPORTANT:\\n• [Sender] — [Subject] → [Label]\\n  └ [Snippet]\\n\\n⚪ LOW PRIORITY:\\n• [Sender] — [Subject] → [Label]\\n  └ [Snippet]\\n```\\n\\nSTEP 6: Update timestamp: echo $(date +%s) > /Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-emmy/last_email_check.timestamp\\n\\nSTEP 7: If no new emails, send a simple confirmation: \\\"✅ Email check done — no new emails\\\" to confirm the cron ran.\",\n        \"model\": \"minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7\"\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n        \"to\": \"8212808444\",\n        \"accountId\": \"emmy\",\n        \"bestEffort\": false\n      },\n      \"deleteAfterRun\": false,\n      \"state\": {\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1777690681948,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 61363,\n        \"lastDelivered\": true,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"delivered\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0,\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1777694281948,\n        \"consecutiveSkipped\": 0\n      },\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1777690743311\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"3f20d0fb-bb39-4216-a3a2-d87613e075f4\",\n      \"name\": \"Memory Dreaming Promotion\",\n      \"description\": \"[managed-by=memory-core.short-term-promotion] Promote weighted short-term recalls into MEMORY.md (limit=10, minScore=0.800, minRecallCount=3, minUniqueQueries=3, recencyHalfLifeDays=14, maxAgeDays=30).\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1775879656205,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 3 * * *\",\n        \"tz\": \"America/New_York\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"__openclaw_memory_core_short_term_promotion_dream__\",\n        \"lightContext\": true\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"none\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1777705200000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1777618800037,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 29955,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"not-requested\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0,\n        \"consecutiveSkipped\": 0\n      },\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1777618829992\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"e63a926f-487e-4bbc-a626-cbf21b1b8670\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:telegram:direct:8212808444\",\n      \"name\": \"Morning Brief Warm-Up\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1775555503054,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"25 5 * * *\",\n        \"tz\": \"America/New_York\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"Wake up. Respond with exactly one word: ok\",\n        \"model\": \"minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 120\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"none\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1777713900000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1777627500026,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 7560,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"not-requested\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0,\n        \"consecutiveSkipped\": 0\n      },\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1777627507586\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"0c8b1d5b-b2fd-45d4-b346-517699a1e000\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:telegram:direct:8212808444\",\n      \"name\": \"Morning Brief\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1775555510727,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"30 5 * * *\",\n        \"tz\": \"America/New_York\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"Run the morning brief skill at ~/.openclaw/skills/morning-brief/SKILL.md. Follow it EXACTLY. Deliver all 7 sections to Telegram chat 8212808444 ONE SECTION AT A TIME. Sections: Header, Weather, Bible Verse, Emails (yesterday+today via Gmail API), Calendar (7 days), Reminders, Suggestions. Do NOT include X/Twitter. Send each section separately via message tool.\",\n        \"model\": \"minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 3600\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n        \"to\": \"8212808444\"\n      },\n      \"failureAlert\": {\n        \"after\": 3,\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n        \"to\": \"8212808444\",\n        \"mode\": \"announce\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1777714200000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1777629049884,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 68110,\n        \"lastDelivered\": true,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"delivered\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0,\n        \"consecutiveSkipped\": 0\n      },\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1777629117994\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"295537b1-3a90-436f-b7de-67d69a5347db\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:telegram:direct:8212808444\",\n      \"name\": \"Flonase Morning Reminder\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1775572842995,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 9 * * *\",\n        \"tz\": \"America/New_York\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"Take your Flonase!\",\n        \"model\": \"minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 3600\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"none\",\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n        \"to\": \"8212808444\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1777726800000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1777640400013,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 133714,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"not-requested\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0,\n        \"consecutiveSkipped\": 0\n      },\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1777640533727\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"ecc194aa-784b-4fd8-bb18-7088d1077903\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:telegram:direct:8212808444\",\n      \"name\": \"Zyrtec Night Reminder\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1775667349513,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 21 * * *\",\n        \"tz\": \"America/New_York\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"next-heartbeat\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"Use the message tool to send exactly this ONE message to Telegram chat 8212808444 and nothing else: '🌙 Hey Bobby! Time to take your Zyrtec 💊'. Do not add any commentary, just send it.\",\n        \"model\": \"minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 3600\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"none\",\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n        \"to\": \"8212808444\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1777770000000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1777683600019,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 181861,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"not-requested\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0,\n        \"consecutiveSkipped\": 0\n      },\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1777683781880\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"6c87956b-dd85-4e4e-8f7d-6c9384c9f9d7\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:telegram:direct:8212808444\",\n      \"name\": \"Weekly Session Cleanup\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1776213884297,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 3 * * 0\",\n        \"tz\": \"America/New_York\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"Run weekly session store maintenance.\\n\\nExecute: `openclaw sessions cleanup --enforce --all-agents`\\n\\nAfter it completes, send a brief Telegram message to Bobby (chat ID: 8212808444) with the result — how many sessions were deleted and MB freed, if reported. Keep it short.\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 300\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"to\": \"8212808444\",\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1777791600000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1777219348688,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 23361,\n        \"lastDelivered\": true,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"delivered\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0\n      },\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1777219372049\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"d0c43bd5-ad9a-4911-b0a9-81b9e4a1e30c\",\n      \"agentId\": \"finn\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:finn:telegram:direct:8212808444\",\n      \"name\": \"Discover 0% APR Ending - Get New Rate\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"deleteAfterRun\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1777584411484,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"at\": \"2026-06-01T14:00:00.000Z\",\n        \"kind\": \"at\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"Bobby — your Discover 0% APR promo ends June 18, 2026! Need to: 1) Find out what the APR becomes after that date, 2) Prioritize paying off the $1,440.22 balance before June 18 if possible.\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 0\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"to\": \"8212808444\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1780322400000\n      },\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1777584411484\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"23feb105-d412-4a3f-b94a-5ff8cb0abcc5\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:telegram:direct:8212808444\",\n      \"name\": \"Next Oil Change July\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"deleteAfterRun\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1775840956738,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"at\": \"2026-07-09T12:00:00.000Z\",\n        \"kind\": \"at\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"🔔 Oil change time! Valvoline estimated July 10, 2026 for your next one. Want me to book it or just remind you closer to the date?\",\n        \"model\": \"minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 120\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n        \"mode\": \"none\",\n        \"to\": \"8212808444\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1783598400000\n      },\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1775840956738\n    }\n  ],\n  \"total\": 10,\n  \"offset\": 0,\n  \"limit\": 10,\n  \"hasMore\": false,\n  \"nextOffset\": null,\n  \"deliveryPreviews\": {\n    \"720739ac-4722-437b-8271-b7c1189c905c\": {\n      \"label\": \"not requested\",\n      \"detail\": \"not requested\"\n    },\n    \"d64702cd-150d-4b69-95b9-d1250b289efb\": {\n      \"label\": \"announce -> telegram:8212808444\",\n      \"detail\": \"explicit\"\n    },\n    \"3f20d0fb-bb39-4216-a3a2-d87613e075f4\": {\n      \"label\": \"none -> last\",\n      \"detail\": \"last -> no route, will fail-closed: Delivering to Telegram requires target <chatId>\"\n    },\n    \"e63a926f-487e-4bbc-a626-cbf21b1b8670\": {\n      \"label\": \"none -> telegram:telegram:8212808444\",\n      \"detail\": \"resolved from last, session agent:main:telegram:direct:8212808444\"\n    },\n    \"0c8b1d5b-b2fd-45d4-b346-517699a1e000\": {\n      \"label\": \"announce -> telegram:8212808444\",\n      \"detail\": \"explicit\"\n    },\n    \"295537b1-3a90-436f-b7de-67d69a5347db\": {\n      \"label\": \"none -> telegram:8212808444\",\n      \"detail\": \"explicit\"\n    },\n    \"ecc194aa-784b-4fd8-bb18-7088d1077903\": {\n      \"label\": \"none -> telegram:8212808444\",\n      \"detail\": \"explicit\"\n    },\n    \"6c87956b-dd85-4e4e-8f7d-6c9384c9f9d7\": {\n      \"label\": \"announce -> telegram:8212808444\",\n      \"detail\": \"explicit\"\n    },\n    \"d0c43bd5-ad9a-4911-b0a9-81b9e4a1e30c\": {\n      \"label\": \"announce -> telegram:8212808444\",\n      \"detail\": \"explicit\"\n    },\n    \"23feb105-d412-4a3f-b94a-5ff8cb0abcc5\": {\n      \"label\": \"none -> telegram:8212808444\",\n      \"detail\": \"explicit\"\n    }\n  }\n}"}],"details":{"persistedDetailsTruncated":true,"originalDetailsBytesAtLeast":8193,"originalDetailKeys":["jobs","total","offset","limit","hasMore","nextOffset","deliveryPreviews"],"total":10},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777691491126}}
{"type":"message","id":"50ad078e","parentId":"3f150a1c","timestamp":"2026-05-02T03:11:57.011Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the original cron job payload. It only checks Gmail. I need to update it to also check iCloud. The iCloud check uses IMAP with curl. I can see from the memory logs that the iCloud check used a message ID checkpoint system.\n\nLet me update the cron job to include iCloud checking. The original cron job ID is `d64702cd-150d-4b69-95b9-d1250b289efb`.\n\nI need to update the payload message to include iCloud checking steps. Let me construct the new message.\n\nFor iCloud, using IMAP over curl:\n- Server: imap.mail.me.com:993\n\n\n- Username: rtg.bobby@icloud.com\n- Password: xleb-qiqv-dged-sydy (stored in security keychain)\n\nTo check for new emails since last check, I'll search for unseen messages and track the latest message ID as a checkpoint so I only notify about truly new emails. Now I'll update the cron job with the iCloud checking steps integrated into the payload.","thinkingSignature":"8305a6075674171808e34b7ed5fe241d6512c82983b69d06dda2def63852083a"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\niCloud connection confirmed ✅ — working via IMAP. Now let me update the cron job to include iCloud checking:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_t720ztm37ab5_1","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"update","jobId":"d64702cd-150d-4b69-95b9-d1250b289efb","patch":{"payload":{"message":"Check for new emails in Bobby's Gmail AND iCloud accounts. Send TWO separate Telegram messages — one for Gmail, one for iCloud.\n\n=== GMAIL CHECK ===\nSTEP 1: Search Gmail for inbox emails from the last 65 minutes:\ngog gmail search 'in:inbox newer_than:65m' --max 50 --account rtg.bobby@gmail.com 2>&1\n\nSTEP 2: Search Gmail for Unroll.me/Unsubscribed emails:\ngog gmail search 'label:\"Unroll.me/Unsubscribed\" newer_than:65m' --max 20 --account rtg.bobby@gmail.com 2>&1\n\nSTEP 3: For any emails in Unroll.me/Unsubscribed:\n- Move to INBOX: gog gmail batch modify <msg_id> --account rtg.bobby@gmail.com --remove \"Unroll.me/Unsubscribed,CATEGORY_PROMOTIONS\" --add INBOX\n\nSTEP 4: For any genuinely new emails:\n- Read the email: gog gmail get <msg_id> --account rtg.bobby@gmail.com\n- Apply labels per Bobby's Email Assistant Skill rules in /Users/bobbygalletta/Desktop/SecondBrain/Email/EMAIL_ASSISTANT_SKILL.md\n- Apply Gmail labels: gog gmail labels add <msg_id> '<LabelName>' --account rtg.bobby@gmail.com\n\nSTEP 5: Send Telegram message to 8212808444 for Gmail:\nIf NEW emails: \"📬 GMAIL — X new email(s)\\n\\n[list of emails]\"\nIf NO new emails: \"📬 GMAIL — No new emails\"\n\nSTEP 6: Update timestamp: echo $(date +%s) > /Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-emmy/last_email_check.timestamp\n\n=== ICLOUD CHECK ===\nSTEP 7: Get iCloud credentials from keychain:\nICLOUD_CREDS=$(security find-generic-password -a \"rtg.bobby@icloud.com\" -s \"emmy-icloud-email\" -w 2>/dev/null)\n\nSTEP 8: Search iCloud INBOX for unseen emails:\ncurl -s --url \"imaps://imap.mail.me.com/INBOX\" --user \"rtg.bobby@icloud.com:$ICLOUD_CREDS\" -X \"SEARCH UNSEEN\" 2>&1\n\nSTEP 9: Read the full envelope for any new messages (parse message numbers from SEARCH results, then fetch ENVELOPE for each):\ncurl -s --url \"imaps://imap.mail.me.com/INBOX\" --user \"rtg.bobby@icloud.com:$ICLOUD_CREDS\" -X \"FETCH <msg_num>:* (ENVELOPE)\" 2>&1\n\nSTEP 10: Track seen emails with a checkpoint file. Load last checkpoint: LAST_ICLOUD=$(cat /Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-emmy/last_icloud_email_id.txt 2>/dev/null || echo \"0\")\n- Compare each message number to LAST_ICLOUD\n- Only process messages with ID > LAST_ICLOUD\n- After processing, update checkpoint: echo <highest_msg_num> > /Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-emmy/last_icloud_email_id.txt\n\nSTEP 11: Send Telegram message to 8212808444 for iCloud:\nIf NEW emails: \"📬 ICLOUD — X new email(s)\\n\\n[list of emails with sender and subject]\"\nIf NO new emails: \"📬 ICLOUD — No new emails\"\n\nSTEP 12: If both accounts have no new emails, it's fine to send two \"no new emails\" messages back to back."}}}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":4616,"output":1116,"cacheRead":44512,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":50244,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777691491129,"responseId":"06449e631172bacec69ce76a17d03111"}}
{"type":"message","id":"622e79e5","parentId":"50ad078e","timestamp":"2026-05-02T03:11:59.727Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_t720ztm37ab5_1","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"id\": \"d64702cd-150d-4b69-95b9-d1250b289efb\",\n  \"agentId\": \"emmy\",\n  \"name\": \"Emmy Email Check\",\n  \"enabled\": true,\n  \"createdAtMs\": 1773960428074,\n  \"schedule\": {\n    \"kind\": \"every\",\n    \"everyMs\": 3600000,\n    \"anchorMs\": 1773961081922\n  },\n  \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n  \"payload\": {\n    \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n    \"message\": \"Check for new emails in Bobby's Gmail AND iCloud accounts. Send TWO separate Telegram messages — one for Gmail, one for iCloud.\\n\\n=== GMAIL CHECK ===\\nSTEP 1: Search Gmail for inbox emails from the last 65 minutes:\\ngog gmail search 'in:inbox newer_than:65m' --max 50 --account rtg.bobby@gmail.com 2>&1\\n\\nSTEP 2: Search Gmail for Unroll.me/Unsubscribed emails:\\ngog gmail search 'label:\\\"Unroll.me/Unsubscribed\\\" newer_than:65m' --max 20 --account rtg.bobby@gmail.com 2>&1\\n\\nSTEP 3: For any emails in Unroll.me/Unsubscribed:\\n- Move to INBOX: gog gmail batch modify <msg_id> --account rtg.bobby@gmail.com --remove \\\"Unroll.me/Unsubscribed,CATEGORY_PROMOTIONS\\\" --add INBOX\\n\\nSTEP 4: For any genuinely new emails:\\n- Read the email: gog gmail get <msg_id> --account rtg.bobby@gmail.com\\n- Apply labels per Bobby's Email Assistant Skill rules in /Users/bobbygalletta/Desktop/SecondBrain/Email/EMAIL_ASSISTANT_SKILL.md\\n- Apply Gmail labels: gog gmail labels add <msg_id> '<LabelName>' --account rtg.bobby@gmail.com\\n\\nSTEP 5: Send Telegram message to 8212808444 for Gmail:\\nIf NEW emails: \\\"📬 GMAIL — X new email(s)\\\\n\\\\n[list of emails]\\\"\\nIf NO new emails: \\\"📬 GMAIL — No new emails\\\"\\n\\nSTEP 6: Update timestamp: echo $(date +%s) > /Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-emmy/last_email_check.timestamp\\n\\n=== ICLOUD CHECK ===\\nSTEP 7: Get iCloud credentials from keychain:\\nICLOUD_CREDS=$(security find-generic-password -a \\\"rtg.bobby@icloud.com\\\" -s \\\"emmy-icloud-email\\\" -w 2>/dev/null)\\n\\nSTEP 8: Search iCloud INBOX for unseen emails:\\ncurl -s --url \\\"imaps://imap.mail.me.com/INBOX\\\" --user \\\"rtg.bobby@icloud.com:$ICLOUD_CREDS\\\" -X \\\"SEARCH UNSEEN\\\" 2>&1\\n\\nSTEP 9: Read the full envelope for any new messages (parse message numbers from SEARCH results, then fetch ENVELOPE for each):\\ncurl -s --url \\\"imaps://imap.mail.me.com/INBOX\\\" --user \\\"rtg.bobby@icloud.com:$ICLOUD_CREDS\\\" -X \\\"FETCH <msg_num>:* (ENVELOPE)\\\" 2>&1\\n\\nSTEP 10: Track seen emails with a checkpoint file. Load last checkpoint: LAST_ICLOUD=$(cat /Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-emmy/last_icloud_email_id.txt 2>/dev/null || echo \\\"0\\\")\\n- Compare each message number to LAST_ICLOUD\\n- Only process messages with ID > LAST_ICLOUD\\n- After processing, update checkpoint: echo <highest_msg_num> > /Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-emmy/last_icloud_email_id.txt\\n\\nSTEP 11: Send Telegram message to 8212808444 for iCloud:\\nIf NEW emails: \\\"📬 ICLOUD — X new email(s)\\\\n\\\\n[list of emails with sender and subject]\\\"\\nIf NO new emails: \\\"📬 ICLOUD — No new emails\\\"\\n\\nSTEP 12: If both accounts have no new emails, it's fine to send two \\\"no new emails\\\" messages back to back.\",\n    \"model\": \"minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7\"\n  },\n  \"delivery\": {\n    \"mode\": \"announce\",\n    \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n    \"to\": \"8212808444\",\n    \"accountId\": \"emmy\",\n    \"bestEffort\": false\n  },\n  \"deleteAfterRun\": false,\n  \"state\": {\n    \"lastRunAtMs\": 1777690681948,\n    \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n    \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n    \"lastDurationMs\": 61363,\n    \"lastDelivered\": true,\n    \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"delivered\",\n    \"consecutiveErrors\": 0,\n    \"nextRunAtMs\": 1777694281948,\n    \"consecutiveSkipped\": 0\n  },\n  \"updatedAtMs\": 1777691517775\n}"}],"details":{"id":"d64702cd-150d-4b69-95b9-d1250b289efb","agentId":"emmy","name":"Emmy Email Check","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1773960428074,"schedule":{"kind":"every","everyMs":3600000,"anchorMs":1773961081922},"sessionTarget":"isolated","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"Check for new emails in Bobby's Gmail AND iCloud accounts. Send TWO separate Telegram messages — one for Gmail, one for iCloud.\n\n=== GMAIL CHECK ===\nSTEP 1: Search Gmail for inbox emails from the last 65 minutes:\ngog gmail search 'in:inbox newer_than:65m' --max 50 --account rtg.bobby@gmail.com 2>&1\n\nSTEP 2: Search Gmail for Unroll.me/Unsubscribed emails:\ngog gmail search 'label:\"Unroll.me/Unsubscribed\" newer_than:65m' --max 20 --account rtg.bobby@gmail.com 2>&1\n\nSTEP 3: For any emails in Unroll.me/Unsubscribed:\n- Move to INBOX: gog gmail batch modify <msg_id> --account rtg.bobby@gmail.com --remove \"Unroll.me/Unsubscribed,CATEGORY_PROMOTIONS\" --add INBOX\n\nSTEP 4: For any genuinely new emails:\n- Read the email: gog gmail get <msg_id> --account rtg.bobby@gmail.com\n- Apply labels per Bobby's Email Assistant Skill rules in /Users/bobbygalletta/Desktop/SecondBrain/Email/EMAIL_ASSISTANT_SKILL.md\n- Apply Gmail labels: gog gmail labels add <msg_id> '<LabelName>' --account rtg.bobby@gmail.com\n\nSTEP 5: Send Telegram message to 8212808444 for Gmail:\nIf NEW emails: \"📬 GMAIL — X new email(s)\\n\\n[list of emails]\"\nIf NO new emails: \"📬 GMAIL — No new emails\"\n\nSTEP 6: Update timestamp: echo $(date +%s) > /Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-emmy/last_email_check.timestamp\n\n=== ICLOUD CHECK ===\nSTEP 7: Get iCloud credentials from keychain:\nICLOUD_CREDS=$(security find-generic-password -a \"rtg.bobby@icloud.com\" -s \"emmy-icloud-email\" -w 2>/dev/null)\n\nSTEP 8: Search iCloud INBOX for unseen emails:\ncurl -s --url \"imaps://imap.mail.me.com/INBOX\" --user \"rtg.bobby@icloud.com:$ICLOUD_CREDS\" -X \"SEARCH UNSEEN\" 2>&1\n\nSTEP 9: Read the full envelope for any new messages (parse message numbers from SEARCH results, then fetch ENVELOPE for each):\ncurl -s --url \"imaps://imap.mail.me.com/INBOX\" --user \"rtg.bobby@icloud.com:$ICLOUD_CREDS\" -X \"FETCH <msg_num>:* (ENVELOPE)\" 2>&1\n\nSTEP 10: Track seen emails with a checkpoint file. Load last checkpoint: LAST_ICLOUD=$(cat /Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-emmy/last_icloud_email_id.txt 2>/dev/null || echo \"0\")\n- Compare each message number to LAST_ICLOUD\n- Only process messages with ID > LAST_ICLOUD\n- After processing, update checkpoint: echo <highest_msg_num> > /Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-emmy/last_icloud_email_id.txt\n\nSTEP 11: Send Telegram message to 8212808444 for iCloud:\nIf NEW emails: \"📬 ICLOUD — X new email(s)\\n\\n[list of emails with sender and subject]\"\nIf NO new emails: \"📬 ICLOUD — No new emails\"\n\nSTEP 12: If both accounts have no new emails, it's fine to send two \"no new emails\" messages back to back.","model":"minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7"},"delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"telegram","to":"8212808444","accountId":"emmy","bestEffort":false},"deleteAfterRun":false,"state":{"lastRunAtMs":1777690681948,"lastRunStatus":"ok","lastStatus":"ok","lastDurationMs":61363,"lastDelivered":true,"lastDeliveryStatus":"delivered","consecutiveErrors":0,"nextRunAtMs":1777694281948,"consecutiveSkipped":0},"updatedAtMs":1777691517775},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777691519727}}
