{"type":"message","id":"69a715b6","parentId":"07580b5a","timestamp":"2026-05-02T03:17:15.755Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I can see from memory that the format was:\n\n```\n📬 NEW MAIL (X new)\n\n🔴 URGENT:\n• [Sender] — [Subject] → [Label]\n  └ [Snippet]\n\n🟡 IMPORTANT:\n• [Sender] — [Subject] → [Label]\n  └ [Snippet]\n\n⚪ LOW PRIORITY:\n• [Sender] — [Subject] → [Label]\n  └ [Snippet]\n```\n\nAnd from SOUL.md:\n**Categories:**\n- 🔴 Bills/Payments — financial obligations, due dates\n- 🟡 Orders — shopping, confirmations, receipts  \n- 🟢 Promotions — newsletters, sales, marketing\n\n\n- 🔵 Updates — service notifications, security alerts\n- ⚫ Other — everything else\n\nNow I need to update the cron job to include this full format with priority/category labels for Gmail, while iCloud uses a simpler sender + subject format.\n","thinkingSignature":"5f4998ffce4d672353eb035bdc7912ddb9b803e6f161e717c1b20d947d0cbafe"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nYes! From your SOUL.md the format was:\n\n```\n📬 NEW MAIL (X new)\n\n🔴 URGENT:\n• [Sender] — [Subject] → [Label]\n  └ [Snippet]\n\n🟡 IMPORTANT:\n• [Sender] — [Subject] → [Label]\n  └ [Snippet]\n\n⚪ LOW PRIORITY:\n• [Sender] — [Subject] → [Label]\n  └ [Snippet]\n```\n\nLet me update the cron to include that. Give me a sec...\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_vtmqju0m2zq6_1","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"update","jobId":"d64702cd-150d-4b69-95b9-d1250b289efb","patch":{"payload":{"message":"Check for new emails in Bobby's Gmail AND iCloud accounts. Send TWO separate Telegram messages — one for Gmail, one for iCloud.\n\n=== GMAIL CHECK ===\nSTEP 1: Search Gmail for inbox emails from the last 65 minutes:\ngog gmail search 'in:inbox newer_than:65m' --max 50 --account rtg.bobby@gmail.com 2>&1\n\nSTEP 2: Search Gmail for Unroll.me/Unsubscribed emails:\ngog gmail search 'label:\"Unroll.me/Unsubscribed\" newer_than:65m' --max 20 --account rtg.bobby@gmail.com 2>&1\n\nSTEP 3: For any emails in Unroll.me/Unsubscribed:\n- Move to INBOX: gog gmail batch modify <msg_id> --account rtg.bobby@gmail.com --remove \"Unroll.me/Unsubscribed,CATEGORY_PROMOTIONS\" --add INBOX\n\nSTEP 4: For any genuinely new emails:\n- Read the email: gog gmail get <msg_id> --account rtg.bobby@gmail.com\n- Categorize per Bobby's rules:\n  🔴 Bills/Payments — financial obligations, due dates (Capital One, Flex, Affirm, Netflix, KUB, etc.)\n  🟡 Orders — shopping, confirmations, receipts\n  🔵 Updates — service notifications, security alerts\n  ⚫ Other — everything else\n\nSTEP 5: Send Telegram message to 8212808444 for Gmail with this format:\nIf NEW emails:\n```\n📬 GMAIL — X new email(s)\n\n🔴 URGENT:\n• [Sender] — [Subject] → [Label]\n  └ [1-line snippet]\n\n🟡 IMPORTANT:\n• [Sender] — [Subject] → [Label]\n  └ [1-line snippet]\n\n⚪ LOW PRIORITY:\n• [Sender] — [Subject] → [Label]\n  └ [1-line snippet]\n```\nIf NO new emails: \"📬 GMAIL — No new emails\"\n\nSTEP 6: Update timestamp: echo $(date +%s) > /Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-emmy/last_email_check.timestamp\n\n=== ICLOUD CHECK ===\nSTEP 7: Get iCloud credentials from keychain:\nICLOUD_CREDS=$(security find-generic-password -a \"rtg.bobby@icloud.com\" -s \"emmy-icloud-email\" -w 2>/dev/null)\n\nSTEP 8: Search iCloud INBOX for unseen emails:\ncurl -s --url \"imaps://imap.mail.me.com/INBOX\" --user \"rtg.bobby@icloud.com:$ICLOUD_CREDS\" -X \"SEARCH UNSEEN\" 2>&1\n\nSTEP 9: Read the full envelope for any new messages (parse message numbers from SEARCH results, then fetch ENVELOPE for each):\ncurl -s --url \"imaps://imap.mail.me.com/INBOX\" --user \"rtg.bobby@icloud.com:$ICLOUD_CREDS\" -X \"FETCH <msg_num>:* (ENVELOPE)\" 2>&1\n\nSTEP 10: Track seen emails with a checkpoint file. Load last checkpoint: LAST_ICLOUD=$(cat /Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-emmy/last_icloud_email_id.txt 2>/dev/null || echo \"0\")\n- Compare each message number to LAST_ICLOUD\n- Only process messages with ID > LAST_ICLOUD\n- After processing, update checkpoint: echo <highest_msg_num> > /Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-emmy/last_icloud_email_id.txt\n\nSTEP 11: Send Telegram message to 8212808444 for iCloud:\nIf NEW emails: \"📬 ICLOUD — X new email(s)\\n\\n[list of emails with sender and subject]\"\nIf NO new emails: \"📬 ICLOUD — No new emails\"\n\nSTEP 12: If both accounts have no new emails, send both \"no new emails\" messages back to back."}}}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2379,"output":1258,"cacheRead":51392,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55029,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777691814040,"responseId":"06449fa6296fbccaf3eb71fc6270942e"}}
{"type":"message","id":"65ab6a50","parentId":"69a715b6","timestamp":"2026-05-02T03:17:24.093Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_vtmqju0m2zq6_1","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"id\": \"d64702cd-150d-4b69-95b9-d1250b289efb\",\n  \"agentId\": \"emmy\",\n  \"name\": \"Emmy Email Check\",\n  \"enabled\": true,\n  \"createdAtMs\": 1773960428074,\n  \"schedule\": {\n    \"kind\": \"every\",\n    \"everyMs\": 3600000,\n    \"anchorMs\": 1773961081922\n  },\n  \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n  \"payload\": {\n    \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n    \"message\": \"Check for new emails in Bobby's Gmail AND iCloud accounts. Send TWO separate Telegram messages — one for Gmail, one for iCloud.\\n\\n=== GMAIL CHECK ===\\nSTEP 1: Search Gmail for inbox emails from the last 65 minutes:\\ngog gmail search 'in:inbox newer_than:65m' --max 50 --account rtg.bobby@gmail.com 2>&1\\n\\nSTEP 2: Search Gmail for Unroll.me/Unsubscribed emails:\\ngog gmail search 'label:\\\"Unroll.me/Unsubscribed\\\" newer_than:65m' --max 20 --account rtg.bobby@gmail.com 2>&1\\n\\nSTEP 3: For any emails in Unroll.me/Unsubscribed:\\n- Move to INBOX: gog gmail batch modify <msg_id> --account rtg.bobby@gmail.com --remove \\\"Unroll.me/Unsubscribed,CATEGORY_PROMOTIONS\\\" --add INBOX\\n\\nSTEP 4: For any genuinely new emails:\\n- Read the email: gog gmail get <msg_id> --account rtg.bobby@gmail.com\\n- Categorize per Bobby's rules:\\n  🔴 Bills/Payments — financial obligations, due dates (Capital One, Flex, Affirm, Netflix, KUB, etc.)\\n  🟡 Orders — shopping, confirmations, receipts\\n  🔵 Updates — service notifications, security alerts\\n  ⚫ Other — everything else\\n\\nSTEP 5: Send Telegram message to 8212808444 for Gmail with this format:\\nIf NEW emails:\\n```\\n📬 GMAIL — X new email(s)\\n\\n🔴 URGENT:\\n• [Sender] — [Subject] → [Label]\\n  └ [1-line snippet]\\n\\n🟡 IMPORTANT:\\n• [Sender] — [Subject] → [Label]\\n  └ [1-line snippet]\\n\\n⚪ LOW PRIORITY:\\n• [Sender] — [Subject] → [Label]\\n  └ [1-line snippet]\\n```\\nIf NO new emails: \\\"📬 GMAIL — No new emails\\\"\\n\\nSTEP 6: Update timestamp: echo $(date +%s) > /Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-emmy/last_email_check.timestamp\\n\\n=== ICLOUD CHECK ===\\nSTEP 7: Get iCloud credentials from keychain:\\nICLOUD_CREDS=$(security find-generic-password -a \\\"rtg.bobby@icloud.com\\\" -s \\\"emmy-icloud-email\\\" -w 2>/dev/null)\\n\\nSTEP 8: Search iCloud INBOX for unseen emails:\\ncurl -s --url \\\"imaps://imap.mail.me.com/INBOX\\\" --user \\\"rtg.bobby@icloud.com:$ICLOUD_CREDS\\\" -X \\\"SEARCH UNSEEN\\\" 2>&1\\n\\nSTEP 9: Read the full envelope for any new messages (parse message numbers from SEARCH results, then fetch ENVELOPE for each):\\ncurl -s --url \\\"imaps://imap.mail.me.com/INBOX\\\" --user \\\"rtg.bobby@icloud.com:$ICLOUD_CREDS\\\" -X \\\"FETCH <msg_num>:* (ENVELOPE)\\\" 2>&1\\n\\nSTEP 10: Track seen emails with a checkpoint file. Load last checkpoint: LAST_ICLOUD=$(cat /Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-emmy/last_icloud_email_id.txt 2>/dev/null || echo \\\"0\\\")\\n- Compare each message number to LAST_ICLOUD\\n- Only process messages with ID > LAST_ICLOUD\\n- After processing, update checkpoint: echo <highest_msg_num> > /Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-emmy/last_icloud_email_id.txt\\n\\nSTEP 11: Send Telegram message to 8212808444 for iCloud:\\nIf NEW emails: \\\"📬 ICLOUD — X new email(s)\\\\n\\\\n[list of emails with sender and subject]\\\"\\nIf NO new emails: \\\"📬 ICLOUD — No new emails\\\"\\n\\nSTEP 12: If both accounts have no new emails, send both \\\"no new emails\\\" messages back to back.\",\n    \"model\": \"minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7\"\n  },\n  \"delivery\": {\n    \"mode\": \"announce\",\n    \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n    \"to\": \"8212808444\",\n    \"accountId\": \"emmy\",\n    \"bestEffort\": false\n  },\n  \"deleteAfterRun\": false,\n  \"state\": {\n    \"lastRunAtMs\": 1777691561471,\n    \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n    \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n    \"lastDurationMs\": 137651,\n    \"lastDelivered\": true,\n    \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"delivered\",\n    \"consecutiveErrors\": 0,\n    \"nextRunAtMs\": 1777694281948,\n    \"consecutiveSkipped\": 0\n  },\n  \"updatedAtMs\": 1777691843675\n}"}],"details":{"id":"d64702cd-150d-4b69-95b9-d1250b289efb","agentId":"emmy","name":"Emmy Email Check","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1773960428074,"schedule":{"kind":"every","everyMs":3600000,"anchorMs":1773961081922},"sessionTarget":"isolated","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"Check for new emails in Bobby's Gmail AND iCloud accounts. Send TWO separate Telegram messages — one for Gmail, one for iCloud.\n\n=== GMAIL CHECK ===\nSTEP 1: Search Gmail for inbox emails from the last 65 minutes:\ngog gmail search 'in:inbox newer_than:65m' --max 50 --account rtg.bobby@gmail.com 2>&1\n\nSTEP 2: Search Gmail for Unroll.me/Unsubscribed emails:\ngog gmail search 'label:\"Unroll.me/Unsubscribed\" newer_than:65m' --max 20 --account rtg.bobby@gmail.com 2>&1\n\nSTEP 3: For any emails in Unroll.me/Unsubscribed:\n- Move to INBOX: gog gmail batch modify <msg_id> --account rtg.bobby@gmail.com --remove \"Unroll.me/Unsubscribed,CATEGORY_PROMOTIONS\" --add INBOX\n\nSTEP 4: For any genuinely new emails:\n- Read the email: gog gmail get <msg_id> --account rtg.bobby@gmail.com\n- Categorize per Bobby's rules:\n  🔴 Bills/Payments — financial obligations, due dates (Capital One, Flex, Affirm, Netflix, KUB, etc.)\n  🟡 Orders — shopping, confirmations, receipts\n  🔵 Updates — service notifications, security alerts\n  ⚫ Other — everything else\n\nSTEP 5: Send Telegram message to 8212808444 for Gmail with this format:\nIf NEW emails:\n```\n📬 GMAIL — X new email(s)\n\n🔴 URGENT:\n• [Sender] — [Subject] → [Label]\n  └ [1-line snippet]\n\n🟡 IMPORTANT:\n• [Sender] — [Subject] → [Label]\n  └ [1-line snippet]\n\n⚪ LOW PRIORITY:\n• [Sender] — [Subject] → [Label]\n  └ [1-line snippet]\n```\nIf NO new emails: \"📬 GMAIL — No new emails\"\n\nSTEP 6: Update timestamp: echo $(date +%s) > /Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-emmy/last_email_check.timestamp\n\n=== ICLOUD CHECK ===\nSTEP 7: Get iCloud credentials from keychain:\nICLOUD_CREDS=$(security find-generic-password -a \"rtg.bobby@icloud.com\" -s \"emmy-icloud-email\" -w 2>/dev/null)\n\nSTEP 8: Search iCloud INBOX for unseen emails:\ncurl -s --url \"imaps://imap.mail.me.com/INBOX\" --user \"rtg.bobby@icloud.com:$ICLOUD_CREDS\" -X \"SEARCH UNSEEN\" 2>&1\n\nSTEP 9: Read the full envelope for any new messages (parse message numbers from SEARCH results, then fetch ENVELOPE for each):\ncurl -s --url \"imaps://imap.mail.me.com/INBOX\" --user \"rtg.bobby@icloud.com:$ICLOUD_CREDS\" -X \"FETCH <msg_num>:* (ENVELOPE)\" 2>&1\n\nSTEP 10: Track seen emails with a checkpoint file. Load last checkpoint: LAST_ICLOUD=$(cat /Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-emmy/last_icloud_email_id.txt 2>/dev/null || echo \"0\")\n- Compare each message number to LAST_ICLOUD\n- Only process messages with ID > LAST_ICLOUD\n- After processing, update checkpoint: echo <highest_msg_num> > /Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-emmy/last_icloud_email_id.txt\n\nSTEP 11: Send Telegram message to 8212808444 for iCloud:\nIf NEW emails: \"📬 ICLOUD — X new email(s)\\n\\n[list of emails with sender and subject]\"\nIf NO new emails: \"📬 ICLOUD — No new emails\"\n\nSTEP 12: If both accounts have no new emails, send both \"no new emails\" messages back to back.","model":"minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7"},"delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"telegram","to":"8212808444","accountId":"emmy","bestEffort":false},"deleteAfterRun":false,"state":{"lastRunAtMs":1777691561471,"lastRunStatus":"ok","lastStatus":"ok","lastDurationMs":137651,"lastDelivered":true,"lastDeliveryStatus":"delivered","consecutiveErrors":0,"nextRunAtMs":1777694281948,"consecutiveSkipped":0},"updatedAtMs":1777691843675},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777691844092}}
