{"type":"message","id":"666fb500","parentId":"209cba09","timestamp":"2026-05-02T07:04:15.757Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_jipeugnvk7ui_1","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"entries\": [\n    {\n      \"ts\": 1777705126304,\n      \"jobId\": \"d64702cd-150d-4b69-95b9-d1250b289efb\",\n      \"action\": \"finished\",\n      \"status\": \"ok\",\n      \"summary\": \"Done. Both accounts checked:\\n\\n- **Gmail** — No new inbox emails in the last 2 hours\\n- **iCloud** — No new unseen emails (last checked ID was 10, still at 10)\\n\\nSent both \\\"no new emails\\\" reports to Telegram. Timestamp updated. 🦋📧\",\n      \"runAtMs\": 1777705086566,\n      \"durationMs\": 39698,\n      \"nextRunAtMs\": 1777708686566,\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"provider\": \"minimax-portal\",\n      \"usage\": {\n        \"input_tokens\": 22546,\n        \"output_tokens\": 932,\n        \"total_tokens\": 22585\n      },\n      \"delivered\": true,\n      \"deliveryStatus\": \"delivered\",\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"intended\": {\n          \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n          \"to\": \"8212808444\",\n          \"accountId\": \"emmy\",\n          \"source\": \"explicit\"\n        },\n        \"resolved\": {\n          \"ok\": true,\n          \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n          \"to\": \"8212808444\",\n          \"accountId\": \"emmy\",\n          \"source\": \"explicit\"\n        },\n        \"messageToolSentTo\": [\n          {\n            \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n            \"to\": \"telegram:8212808444\"\n          },\n          {\n            \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n            \"to\": \"telegram:8212808444\"\n          }\n        ],\n        \"fallbackUsed\": false,\n        \"delivered\": true\n      },\n      \"sessionId\": \"3f8e99d5-c0c8-4527-8990-59455a7995db\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:emmy:cron:d64702cd-150d-4b69-95b9-d1250b289efb:run:3f8e99d5-c0c8-4527-8990-59455a7995db\"\n    },\n   