 \\\"emmy\\\"), and X Developer Platform receipt ($10).\\n\\n**iCloud:** No new emails.\",\n      \"runAtMs\": 1777697886536,\n      \"durationMs\": 50563,\n      \"nextRunAtMs\": 1777701486536,\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"provider\": \"minimax-portal\",\n      \"usage\": {\n        \"input_tokens\": 30704,\n        \"output_tokens\": 2823,\n        \"total_tokens\": 30703\n      },\n      \"delivered\": true,\n      \"deliveryStatus\": \"delivered\",\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"intended\": {\n          \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n          \"to\": \"8212808444\",\n          \"accountId\": \"emmy\",\n          \"source\": \"explicit\"\n        },\n        \"resolved\": {\n          \"ok\": true,\n          \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n          \"to\": \"8212808444\",\n          \"accountId\": \"emmy\",\n          \"source\": \"explicit\"\n        },\n        \"messageToolSentTo\": [\n          {\n            \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n            \"to\": \"telegram:8212808444\"\n          },\n          {\n            \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n            \"to\": \"telegram:8212808444\"\n          }\n        ],\n        \"fallbackUsed\": false,\n        \"delivered\": true\n      },\n      \"sessionId\": \"01f602c6-a7eb-46d8-89a8-357b9b57a601\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:emmy:cron:d64702cd-150d-4b69-95b9-d1250b289efb:run:01f602c6-a7eb-46d8-89a8-357b9b57a601\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"ts\": 1777694382045,\n      \"jobId\": \"d64702cd-150d-4b69-95b9-d1250b289efb\",\n      \"action\": \"finished\",\n      \"status\": \"ok\",\n      \"summary\": \"📬 **Gmail:** Found 2 new emails — Apple security alert (app-specific password generated — if that's you, all good) and X Developer Platform $10 receipt.\\n\\n📬 **iCloud:** No new emails.\\n\\nTimestamp updated. Both summaries sent to Telegram. ✅\",\n      \"runAtMs\": 1777694286525,\n      \"durationMs\": 95512,\n      \"nextRunAtMs\": 1777697886525,\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"provider\": \"minimax-portal\",\n      \"usage\": {\n        \"input_tokens\": 27359,\n        \"output_tokens\": 2181,\n        \"total_tokens\": 27373\n      },\n      \"delivered\": true,\n      \"deliveryStatus\": \"delivered\",\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"intended\": {\n          \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n          \"to\": \"8212808444\",\n          \"accountId\": \"emmy\",\n          \"source\": \"explicit\"\n        },\n        \"resolved\": {\n          \"ok\": true,\n          \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n          \"to\": \"8212808444\",\n          \"accountId\": \"emmy\",\n          \"source\": \"explicit\"\n        },\n        \"messageToolSentTo\": [\n          {\n            \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n            \"to\": \"8212808444\"\n          },\n          {\n            \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n            \"to\": \"8212808444\"\n          }\n        ],\n        \"fallbackUsed\": false,\n        \"delivered\": true\n      },\n      \"sessionId\": \"591a1817-b843-412f-a4d8-1b0f070ccd56\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:emmy:cron:d64702cd-150d-4b69-95b9-d1250b289efb:run:591a1817-b843-412f-a4d8-1b0f070ccd56\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"ts\": 1777691699129,\n      \"jobId\": \"d64702cd-150d-4b69-95b9-d1250b289efb\",\n      \"action\": \"finished\",\n      \"status\": \"ok\",\n      \"summary\": \"Done! Here's the summary:\\n\\n**Gmail:** 2 new emails (both from the last 65 min):\\n- 🔵 **Apple** — App-specific password was generated (security alert — flagged for Bobby to verify)\\n- 🔵 **X Developer Platform** — Receipt for $10.00 (billing)\\n\\nAlso moved 5 Unroll.me/Unsubscribed emails back to Inbox for Bobby to review.\\n\\n**iCloud:** No new emails.\\n\\nBoth Telegram messages sent. ✅\",\n      \"runAtMs\": 1777691561471,\n      \"durationMs\": 137651,\n      \"nextRunAtMs\": 1777694281948,\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"provider\": \"minimax-portal\",\n      \"usage\": {\n        \"input_tokens\": 27861,\n        \"output_tokens\