   \"jobId\": \"d64702cd-150d-4b69-95b9-d1250b289efb\",\n      \"action\": \"finished\",\n      \"status\": \"ok\",\n      \"summary\": \"📬 EMAIL CHECK FAILED — Authentication Issue\\n\\nHey Bobby, the hourly email check just ran but hit an authentication problem:\\n\\n🔴 **Gmail Access Denied**\\n- gog CLI: No OAuth token stored (keyring is empty)\\n- Python script: Refresh token is invalid/expired\\n\\n**What you need to do:**\\n1. **Re-authenticate gog:** Run `gog auth add rtg.bobby@gmail.com` in Terminal - it will open a browser for OAuth\\n2. **Or update credentials:** The refresh token in `~/.config/gmail_oauth/credentials.json` has been revoked\\n\\nOnce re-authenticated, the hourly checks will resume automatically. Sorry for the interruption! 🦋📧\",\n      \"runAtMs\": 1776715097337,\n      \"durationMs\": 549742,\n      \"nextRunAtMs\": 1776718697337,\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"provider\": \"minimax-portal\",\n      \"usage\": {\n        \"input_tokens\": 234293,\n        \"output_tokens\": 5300,\n        \"total_tokens\": 28356\n      },\n      \"delivered\": true,\n      \"deliveryStatus\": \"delivered\",\n      \"sessionId\": \"df615c1e-d699-4381-ad22-b57b7b3e4728\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:emmy:cron:d64702cd-150d-4b69-95b9-d1250b289efb:run:df615c1e-d699-4381-ad22-b57b7b3e4728\"\n    },\n    {\n\n⚠️ [... middle content omitted — showing head and tail ...]\n\n        \"output_tokens\": 153,\n        \"total_tokens\": 17373\n      },\n      \"delivered\": true,\n      \"deliveryStatus\": \"delivered\",\n      \"sessionId\": \"ea8d99e5-0eed-45ac-868f-5cc9fcefdde8\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:emmy:cron:d64702cd-150d-4b69-95b9-d1250b289efb:run:ea8d99e5-0eed-45ac-868f-5cc9fcefdde8\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"ts\": 1776576562803,\n      \"jobId\": \"d64702cd-150d-4b69-95b9-d1250b289efb\",\n      \"action\": \"finished\",\n      \"status\": \"ok\",\n      \"summary\": \"✅ Email check done — no new emails.\",\n      \"runAtMs\": 17765765